Title: 1. People
Write-Up Text: The people are lit up with their social media posts. One demands we call Dan who has everything under control. Another highlights the Australian government's outrage as its extensive Parliament House renovation costs taxpayers over 90 million dollars across three years. The remaining people tag their mates with a mysterious link which is unclear in context and purpose. Despite the confusion one post supporting the overhaul of Australia's gas tax system gained support - calling out the unfairness between ordinary Canberrans and global gas companies!
